column5: Any reports or info on Tennant Lake Ontario
Dave, we are booked for early June. I would appreciate any information you can provide before our trip next summer. Good luck! Fish On! Hooks

You will have a blast that time of the year I am sure the fish will be stacked at the in flowing river mouth and up the river. Our group has fished this system (6) times but we stayed on Kap but fished Tennant also. Hopefully the water level is such that you will be able to go to Kap and Melchett also a little lake named Tester. Good fishing and good luck.
Just got back from Stewart, just up river from Tennant. The water is the lowest I have ever seen in the last 15 years. There can't be much water going down the rapids.

Chadder, we are there the week after you. We would appreciate any notes or information you could leave in the cabin. You could leave a couple beers and some bourbon too, if you don't mind () We have six guys in our group. Fish On! Hooks

i unfortunately have to cancel my trip,my long time friend/fishinh partner is very ill and we cant make a solid coomitment....i have not even contacted the outfitter yet....next step if anyone is interested in june 1-8 2018....feel free to grab it up
